title: NASCAR picks driver-preferred low-downforce package for 2016
text: Photo: Terry Renna, AP Matt Kenseth (20) and Kyle Busch (18) lead the field at the start of the NASCAR Sprint Cup series auto race at Charlotte Motor Speedway in Concord, N.C., Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. Matt Kenseth (20) and Kyle Busch (18) lead the field at the start... CHARLOTTE, N.C. (AP) — NASCAR's ever-changing plans to design a rules package that improves the racing has finally landed on the configuration the drivers desperately wanted.
